name: __EQuartzCommandDelegateSubType
doc: An enumeration for specifying different TYPES of delegates

CommandOnFailedToQueue: The command will not execute (i.e. Clock doesn't exist or PlayQuantized failed concurrency)
CommandOnQueued: The command has been passed to the Audio Render Thread
CommandOnCanceled: The command was stopped before it could execute
CommandOnAboutToStart: execute off this to be in sync w/ sound starting
CommandOnStarted: the command was just executed on the Audio Render Thrtead
